Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}『WOLF字幕組』      (www.wolfsub.com)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高塔幻蹤赤影見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鵺鳥啼曉展翅翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白刃凜凜金鐵鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天道前程路茫茫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是從棲息在亞馬遜的眼鏡蛇毒液中提取神經毒素後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加以改良的成品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短時間內是無法回復的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽說過古代文豪托爾斯泰的名言麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在無限發展的文明中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果人的死是無意義的 那麼生也同樣無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要超越這個局限 成為操縱生死之人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的頭顱是不可或缺！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來傷口的愈合力的確變弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這肉體也差不多快到極限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被它發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它馬上就要到你附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右後方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎 右上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正後方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎 九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不見它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫得很痛苦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區一個木偶還想著做人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換上九郎的頭顱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓究極的生命體誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,匹敵神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想明明就要實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟來妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻出自己去成為究極生命的僕從吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是我想得到九郎的頭顱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到最後卻是自己的頭顱被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有過去的自己的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷失自我的感覺纏繞著我伴我走過一天又一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個謎終於要解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須去見她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了這最後一刻我努力到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 這種感覺是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些捉摸不透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到還有盲點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然無法很好地表達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道還有我不知道的秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被騙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被她？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是被我自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說 被命運？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什麼才是原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你我不辭辛勞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臥底埴輪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你我等來了九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼 你應該知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是為了你我才活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看到的是你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剩下我們兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要的是我的身體對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼 久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了那個男人 為了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才創造了我對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真正的目的 是九郎對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法勝任你旅行的伴侶對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒資格對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:16:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 從來就
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒愛過我對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從沒愛過我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧 九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見到的黑蜜 是幻影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰側的那三顆小痣也是我的幻覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 瞧你那臉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也會有這種表情嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎

